name: Sri Yantra Prints III &IV
description:
Sri Yantra III:
Beautiful 2 colour screen print, turquoise inks overlaid with gold. 
23cm x 23cm on Southbank Smooth paper.

Sri Yantra IV:
Beautiful 3 colour screen print, blended purple and turquoise inks overlaid with gold. 23cm x 23cm on Southbank Smooth paper.

© Carla Sam 2010

Sealed in a Poly bag with sturdy backing card and posted in a padded envelope to ensure it arrives in mint condition.

name: GREEN MAN II editioned series
description:
Beautifully intricate, hand crafted 4 colour silkscreen print of the Green Man II series . Limited edition of 30 prints per run/paperstock  © Carla Sam 2010.

Available in a range of paper stocks, in various sizes (refer to notes on main image and below):

White paper stock (21x21cm)
Earthy Brown paper stock (23x23cm)
Sage Green paper stock (23x23cm)
Spring Green paper stock (21x21cm)


Packaged in A4 envelope backed with sturdy card and dispatched same day if ordered before noon, to reach you in mint condition!

Limited edition of 30 prints per paper stock in the Green Man I series © Carla Sam 2010.
